# Vercel deploys ONLY the static dashboard. Everything Python — the engine,
# the serverless function, the FastAPI/CLI backend — is excluded so Vercel's
# Python/FastAPI auto-detection never fires. The dashboard renders the bundled
# real snapshot; for live data on a hosted deploy, run the backend elsewhere
# and point VITE_API_URL at it (see README).
.venv/
_live/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
*.egg-info/
.github/
tests/
scripts/
api/
src/
requirements.txt
pyproject.toml
dashboard/node_modules/
dashboard/dist/
